    {
      "id": "e4832b90-6922-49f1-8220-5d85225ab73e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The findings show that that some patterns of SRL can, indeed, generalize between different courses and it is even possible to find some relationship between interaction and performance. However, the generalization to other contexts requires a reduction in complexity of the models, whihc may lead to a situation where all you have is too much of a simplification.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "e4832b90-6922-49f1-8220-5d85225ab73e",
